com.jrfom.gw2.api.model.events

Interface Location

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EventCylinderLocation, EventLocation, EventPolyLocation, EventSphereLocation

    @Gw2ApiVersion(value="v1")
public interface Location

    A Location describes where an Event takes place in the game world. There are three possible location types:

    • EventCylinderLocation
    • EventPolyLocation
    • EventSphereLocation
